features: 【Real-Time Tracking & Precise Positioning】 The car tracker using GPS/LBS/AGPS multiple fast and precise positioning technology, even if it is stationary, it will never be offline. The GPS tracker device positioning accuracy can reach 5m. Download the free APP to track motorcycle, truck, taxi in real time. NOTE: You need to purchase a local SIM card network to insert into the tracker (SIM Card Not Include).

【Multi-Function Alarm & Electronic Fence】Real-time location device built-in backup battery and double antennas, support overspeed alarm, power outage alarm, low power alarm, displacement alarm, fence entry alarm, cross-border alarm and other functions. With the custom range of the electronic fence, you can track vehicle safety anytime, anywhere.

【Historical Track Playback & Smart Storage】 Waterproof locator can play back the driving track within 180 days, including the route passed, the location and time of stay, and grasp the historical dynamics at a glance. When there is no mobile phone signal, the data is stored in the GPS, and it will be retransmitted when there is a signal, so that no details will be missed.

【Multi-Vehicle Management & Street View 3D】 You can view multiple vehicles with trackers installed under one account, which is convenient for unified management. When you see the exact location of your pet but don't know the route, you can turn on Street View mode to see nearby buildings.

【After Sales & Packaging】Senpinkboo offers 30-day unconditional returns, if you have any questions, please feel free to contact our customer service. Package included: 1 X GPS Tracker, 1 X Double Sided Sticker, 1 X User Manual.
